72682ff15","tid":844360,"uid":163024,"like":1,"dislike":4,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-01T23:37:23.000Z","msg":"用正字 =/= 吹毛求疵<br />\n始終係用梗電腦打字而非手寫<br />\n啲人啲要求高到好似寫梗中文作文咁<br />\n都痴撚線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3da7b3bd5150617fa64fbe2ffb3a4b3b8a743ffc","tid":844360,"uid":163024,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"5a7734ea874bd736bb2cba1b2e50a4b32b68e17f","tid":844360,"uid":163024,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"quote":{"pid":"a42f0b05e7fc708ec01f95327ac4da2be35f8c11","tid":844360,"uid":161159,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"39eba4226c32b6452e876dd5bfa81adeed702fa7","tid":844360,"uid":163024,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-01T23:18:26.000Z","msg":"所以我話喺「文章唔影響讀者閱讀體驗」嘅情況下"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-01T23:22:18.000Z","msg":"屌邊個定義到影唔影響<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 你既然認同會造成閱讀不便就打好啲字啦"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-01T23:24:43.000Z","msg":"大部分有基礎閱讀能力嘅人都分辨到<br />\n苦海無涯 回頭是岸 施主唔好再執迷不悟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-01T23:50:22.000Z","msg":"可能小弟我表達得唔清楚<br />\n<br />\n我唔係想鼓吹火星文/殘體字/詞不達意<br />\n而係如果一篇文大部分人都可以好自然好通順咁樣讀完<br />\n而呢個時候又有條友不知所謂咁樣出黎指鳩人地冇用正字<br />\n<br />\n我覺得呢種行為根本就係<span style=\"color: red;\">衝出黎柒</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"56e6a470ac5e026e5a2ece621a36cb80e0f1f198","tid":844360,"uid":198583,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-02T00:43:28.000Z","msg":"戇字都唔識打有咩討論空間"},{"pid":"2612c7e5a061f8aea8b5d34dbe337371a875ba11","tid":844360,"uid":59920,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-02T00:45:49.000Z","msg":"( ̀⌄ ́)岩牙"},{"pid":"ea23ea162cb074401769dae611fe17c9499699ea","tid":844360,"uid":175623,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-02T01:02:56.000Z","msg":"Iphone仔表示十分認同"}]}